{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Memory Modules API",
    "description": "Refactored: Episodic + Semantic + Session memory backend for AI chatbots.\n\n**Memory layers**\n- **Session (Working Memory)**: in-thread conversation context, auto-titled and summarised\n- **Episodic**: Qdrant vector store \u2014 past turn summaries, recalled by similarity\n- **Semantic**: Neo4j knowledge graph \u2014 extracted entities and facts\n\n**Chatbot integration**: call `/memory/context` to get a ready-to-inject system prompt block.",
    "version": "2.0.0"
  },
